{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/Hiraeth-slogan.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover <strong>\u2635 HIRAETH</strong> - A gripping sci-fi survival experience where you awaken on the forsaken planet <strong>Ahra Prime</strong>. Navigate through its harsh, diverse landscapes filled with secrets and dangers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay Modes:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ETERNAL Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-sandbox.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into an endless survival sandbox where your skills are your only ally. Survive, explore, and uncover lore that deepens with each playthrough.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>REVELATIONS Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-rich-story.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a narrative-driven journey, uncovering the mysteries of Ahra Prime guided by the enigmatic Charon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hand-Crafted Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-open-world.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scour the planet for resources, facing environmental hazards and predators. Every journey is a test of survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deep Survival Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-survival.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage hunger, hydration, health, and equipment durability in a system tailored for both novice and seasoned survivors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Crafting &amp; Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-eva-suit.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master crafting to create essential gear and upgrade your EVA suit for better survival odds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Progressive Skills &amp; Perks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-port.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn skills and perks that enhance your abilities, making each survival attempt more strategic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/PitchWeather.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/SnowBag.gif?t=1734486365\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Companions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-compagnion.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose between a quirky alien slug or a high-tech droid to assist in your adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/PitchFBA.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/PickRifle.gif?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/PitchVechicles.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/DriveShort20.gif?t=1734486365\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>For New Players:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-training.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Training Course:</strong> A dedicated center to learn the ropes, ensuring everyone can grasp the game's unique mechanics.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Audio Experience:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-soundtrack.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmospheric Soundtrack: </strong>Immerse yourself in the desolation of Ahra Prime with an electronic score that complements the game's mood.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Why \u2635 HIRAETH?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're a lone wolf tackling the planet's perils head-on or a strategist avoiding conflict, <strong>\u2635 HIRAETH</strong> offers freedom in survival. With every playthrough unique due to randomization and player choices, your saga on Ahra Prime will be as unpredictable as the planet itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/hiraeth-game-watcher.png?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Remember, on Ahra Prime,\u00a0</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>&quot;wise men speak, and fools decide.&quot;</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Which will you be?</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WHY SINGLE PLAYER?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Advantages Of Single Player Games Over Multiplayer:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Engaging Storyline:</strong>\u00a0Single player games often offer deeper and more complex narratives that can provide emotional experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 No Dependency on Others:\u00a0</strong>You don't have to wait for other players or worry about their skills or behavior. The game progresses at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Full Control:\u00a0</strong>You have complete control over the gameplay, allowing you to explore the game's world and uncover its secrets at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 No Connection Issues:</strong>\u00a0No need for a stable internet connection, meaning you can play anytime, anywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Personalized Experience:</strong>\u00a0Single player games often offer greater opportunities for personalization and individual approaches to gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Achievements and Challenges:</strong>\u00a0Focus on individual achievements and challenges, which can be satisfying to accomplish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Peace and Quiet:</strong>\u00a0No risk of harassment or toxic behavior from other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2705 Slower Aging of the Game:\u00a0</strong>Single player games age more slowly, as players are willing to return to them even after many years. Multiplayer games typically have a shorter lifespan, dependent on community activity.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WHY HIRAETH STANDS OUT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many survival games follow a familiar formula: chop trees, build structures, craft, and survive. Hiraeth breaks this mold by offering a unique and immersive survival experience that keeps the fun and flow intact.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Innovative Survival Mechanics:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eat, Drink, Rest, Heal, Recharge, Manage Oxygen.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always monitor your EVA Suit's air supply.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage and maintain gear and health.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Four Difficulty Levels:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wayfarer:\u00a0</strong>Easy, focus on story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drifter:\u00a0</strong>Normal, balanced challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Outcast:\u00a0</strong>Hard, for veterans.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Void Rider:</strong>\u00a0Nightmare, extreme challenge.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Player Freedom:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple playstyles:</strong>\u00a0aggressive or strategic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Randomization</strong>, accessibility options, rougelite elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique gameplay each session</strong>.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Accessibility and Elegance:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adjustable\u00a0<strong>parental settings</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed<strong>\u00a0for diverse skill levels</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Avoids unnecessary gore</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/EXIT.jpg?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/DaySpeed.gif?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2646160/extras/ramp1.gif?t=1734486365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_im